ice and exploitation team in his bar."},{"name":"Kate Liu","aliases":["Kate"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4","currentLocation":"Distinguished Hyacinth Lounge","description":"Fourth generation owner of the Distinguished Hyacinth Lounge.","relationships":[{"character":"Javier Liu","relationship":"grandfather"}],"recentEvents":"Serving drinks to Miller and Havelock."},{"name":"Cassio Ramachandra","aliases":["Ramachandra"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4","currentLocation":"Distinguished Hyacinth Lounge","description":"Star Helix Security's top officer, working for Amunet, known for his sharp mind and a penchant for using Miller's alias.","relationships":[{"character":"Josephus Miller","relationship":"fellow Star Helix Security agent, co-worker"},{"character":"Yevgeny Cobb","relationship":"fellow homicide officer"},{"character":"Javier Liu","relationship":"acquaintance"}],"recentEvents":"Present in the Distinguished Hyacinth Lounge when the alert came in."},{"name":"Josephus Miller","aliases":["Miller"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4","currentLocation":"Distinguished Hyacinth Lounge","description":"Earther and Star Helix Security agent, now on a personal mission assigned by Shaddid.","relationships":[{"character":"William Ochoa","relationship":"fellow homicide officer"},{"character":"Cassio Ramachandra","relationship":"fellow Star Helix Security agent, co-worker"},{"character":"Donna Shader","relationship":"fellow Star Helix Security agent"},{"character":"Chrisjen Avasarala","relationship":"former diplomat"}],"recentEvents":"At the lounge with Havelock and responding to Shaddid's emergency message."},{"name":"Pramod Rao","aliases":["Shaddid"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4","currentLocation":"Star Helix Command Center","description":"Captain of Star Helix, Shaddid leads security operations and is a critical figure in Amunet’s corporate hierarchy.","relati