ise and calm demeanor.","relationships":[{"character":"James Holden","relationship":"Captain and friend"},{"character":"Naomi Nagata","relationship":"First officer and friend"},{"character":"Amos Burton","relationship":"Chief Engineer and friend"}],"recentEvents":"Alex was monitoring the sensors during the battle when the Donnager was hit by a torpedo, warning the crew about the upcoming impact."},{"name":"Lopez","importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter: Tug of War","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A mariner with the Rocinante, primarily a medic and a pilot.","relationships":[{"character":"James Holden","relationship":"Captain and crew member"}],"recentEvents":"Lopez is not mentioned in this chapter."},{"name":"A marine officer","importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter: Tug of War","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A naval intelligence officer on the Donnager who questioned James Holden.","relationships":[{"character":"James Holden","relationship":"Interviewed subject"}],"recentEvents":"The officer questioned Holden and left his quarters during the battle."},{"name":"Dawes","aliases":["Agent Dawes"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Nemesis","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"An agent of the Outer Planets Alliance (OPA), who visits Eros Station with concerns regarding Josephus Miller's investigation.","relationships":[{"character":"Josephus Miller","relationship":"Interviewed subject"}],"recentEvents":"Attempted to convince Miller to abandon his search for Julie Mao, indicating Dawes' awareness of a growing crisis situation."}],"locations":[{"name":"The Scopuli","aliases":["Scopuli"],"arc":"Piracy","description":"A ship that has been attacked and abandoned, located in the belt between planets.","recentEvents":"Jim and Amos investigate the ship and discover a fake distress beacon that led to the discovery of the derelict ship.","relationships":[{"location":"Knight","relationship":"Invest