 unidentified ships and engages in a brutal battle with point defense systems and gauss turrets active. The ship is hit by a torpedo, and internal damage is caused.","relationships":[{"location":"Unknown ships","relationship":"Engaged in battle against"},{"location":"Knight","relationship":"Pursuing the Knight ship"},{"location":"Outer Planets Alliance","relationship":"The OPA warns about the influence of this battlecruiser"}]},{"name":"Eros","arc":"Power Struggle","description":"A station in the asteroid belt, part of the setting where mining activities and social tensions among Belters play out.","recentEvents":"Miller is advised to take precautions and leave the station, suggesting heightened tensions and potential threats.","relationships":[{"location":"Ceres","relationship":"Part of the same asteroid belt, interconnected in terms of mining operations and political issues."}]},{"name":"Hangar Bay","arc":"War","description":"A part of the Canterbury where spacecraft can be stored and launched.","recentEvents":"Survivors attempt to escape in a commandeered corvette, while facing enemy boarders.","relationships":[{"location":"Canterbury","relationship":"Part of the Canterbury"}]},{"name":"Ganymede","arc":"Conflict","description":"A large moon of Jupiter, significant for its role in interplanetary trade and being a staging point for operations involving Ceres.","recentEvents":"Serves as the destination for the Black Cat freighter carrying stolen police equipment from Ceres.","relationships":[{"location":"Ceres","relationship":"The Black Cat freighter transported stolen police equipment and personnel to Ganymede from Ceres."}]},{"name":"Tachi","arc":"The Donnager Event","description":"A salvaged MCRN gunboat now in Jim Holden's possession.","recentEvents":"Jim Holden and his crew use Tachi to escape the battle and seek refuge from the MCRN.","relationships":[{"location":"MCRN","relationship":"Currently evading"}]}],"arcs":[{"name":"Navigating Martian Interception","s