 Last Serenity","currentLocation":"Canterbury","description":"The communications officer aboard the Canterbury.","relationships":[{"character":"Jim Holden","relationship":"Communications Officer"},{"character":"William Orlowski","relationship":"Father"},{"character":"Ava Tukunbo","relationship":"Navigator"},{"character":"Mark Paj","relationship":"Engineer"}],"recentEvents":"Becca sent out a message to the broken ship and informed Ceres about the unexpected detour."},{"name":"Amos Burton","aliases":["Amos","Amos 'Tango Down' Burton","Tango Down","Amo","A.B.","Mister Burton","Mr. Burton","Mechanical Genius","Chief"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 3","currentLocation":"Eros","description":"Chief Engineer of the Rocinante, a former professional wrestler with a sarcastic sense of humor.","relationships":[{"character":"James Holden","relationship":"Captain"},{"character":"Naomi Nagata","relationship":"Navigational Officer"},{"character":"Alex Kamal","relationship":"Pilot"},{"character":"Miller","relationship":"Detective"}],"recentEvents":"Provided input regarding the logistics and risks associated with the investigation of BA834024112."},{"name":"Javier Liu","aliases":["Javier"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4","currentLocation":"Distinguished Hyacinth Lounge","description":"A structural engineer from Tycho, now with his grandchildren running his bar the Distinguished Hyacinth Lounge.","relationships":[{"character":"Cassio Ramachandra","relationship":"acquaintance"}],"recentEvents":"Talking with members of the vice and exploitation team in his bar."},{"name":"Kate Liu","aliases":["Kate"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4","currentLocation":"Distinguished Hyacinth Lounge","description":"Fourth generation owner of the Distinguished Hyacinth Lounge.","relationships":[{"character":"Javier Liu","relationship":"grandfather"}],"recentEvents":"Serving drinks to Miller and Havelock."},{"name":"