plex conspiracy."},{"name":"Radiation Shelter Discoveries","status":"active","characters":["Holden","Miller"],"summary":"Holden and Miller discover that the radiation shelters are laced with gas and radiation, leading to the conclusion that the population may have been infected or poisoned."},{"name":"Escape from Eros","status":"active","characters":["James Holden","Josephus Miller"],"summary":"Miller and Holden successfully navigate through Eros to their hideout but discover that Naomi, Alex, and Amos are missing."},{"name":"Miller and Holden's Dilemma","status":"active","characters":["Holden","Miller"],"summary":"Holden and Miller are now facing immediate danger as they attempt to navigate through the violence and reach Holden's ship, searching for essential medication."},{"name":"Miller and Holden's Escape from Eros","status":"active","characters":["Miller","Holden"],"summary":"Miller and Holden successfully navigate the chaos of Eros, following the withdrawing mercenaries in their attempt to escape the deteriorating situation."}],"summary":"Miller and Holden navigate the chaos of Eros as an experiment goes awry, with mercenaries suddenly withdrawing their guard, presenting a potential path to escape. They prepare to move towards the port, hoping to find answers and a means to survival."},"model":"qwen2.5:14b","appVersion":"dev"},{"index":35,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"Juliette Andromeda Mao","aliases":["Julie Mao","Jules","Razorback","N/A","Muss","Captain","Mr. Jim","Jim Holden","Captain Shaddid","Jim","James Holden","Boss","Captain Holden","William Orlowski","Havelock","Billy Havelock","Wayne Havelock","Candace","Willis Havelock","Detective Muss","Krista Muss","Miller","Joseph Michael Miller","Julie","Detective","Earth Dog","Joseph Miller","the cop","Josephus Miller","Cop","James Miller","Joseph","old man","cerebral cop","cop","peace officer","Detective Miller","The man with the hat","Joseph Sematimba","partner","Juliette Mao","Cap&#39;n","none","Anderson 