":"Holden and Miller seek refuge on their ship after a harrowing escape"}]},{"name":"Hangar Bay","arc":"War","description":"A part of the Canterbury where spacecraft can be stored and launched.","recentEvents":"Survivors attempt to escape in a commandeered corvette, while facing enemy boarders.","relationships":[{"location":"Canterbury","relationship":"Part of the Canterbury"}]},{"name":"Ganymede","arc":"Conflict","description":"A large moon of Jupiter, significant for its role in interplanetary trade and being a staging point for operations involving Ceres.","recentEvents":"Serves as the destination for the Black Cat freighter carrying stolen police equipment from Ceres.","relationships":[{"location":"Ceres","relationship":"The Black Cat freighter transported stolen police equipment and personnel to Ganymede from Ceres."}]},{"name":"Tachi","arc":"The Donnager Event","description":"A salvaged MCRN gunboat now in Jim Holden's possession.","recentEvents":"Jim Holden and his crew use Tachi to escape the battle and seek refuge from the MCRN.","relationships":[{"location":"MCRN","relationship":"Currently evading"}]},{"name":"Tycho Station","aliases":["Tycho Manufacturing and Engineering Concern"],"arc":"The Expansion","description":"A large orbital station circling a planet, serving as a hub for space travel and commerce.","recentEvents":"The crew is spending time on Tycho to rest and gather information before deciding their next steps.","relationships":[{"location":"Rocinante","relationship":"The crew visits and repairs the ship docked at Tycho"}]},{"name":"Rocinante","aliases":["Roci"],"arc":"Deep Space Rescue","description":"A spacecraft where the crew lives and conducts their missions, often serving as a base of operations.","recentEvents":"Amos greets the injured Holden and Miller, who are returning after a difficult mission.","relationships":[{"location":"Eros","relationship":"The team returns here after a perilous escape from an asteroid filled with turmoil"}]},{"