":"Holden and Miller are now facing immediate danger as they attempt to navigate through the violence and reach Holden's ship, searching for essential medication."},{"name":"Miller and Holden's Escape from Eros","status":"active","characters":["Miller","Holden"],"summary":"Miller and Holden successfully navigate the chaos of Eros, following the withdrawing mercenaries in their attempt to escape the deteriorating situation."},{"name":"Holden and Miller Escape Eros","status":"active","characters":["Holden","Miller","Amos"],"summary":"Holden and Miller narrowly escape Eros's conflict by donning stolen armor and making a harrowing dash towards the Rocinante, with Amos arriving at critical moment to provide extraction and immediate safety."},{"name":"Personal Relationships on Rocinante","status":"active","characters":["Miller","Holden","Naomi"],"summary":"Miller advises Holden on his relationship with Naomi, suggesting he invest more effort into understanding and pursuing her."},{"name":"The Scopuli Mystery","status":"active","characters":["Holden","Amos","Naomi","Alex","Miller"],"summary":"The mystery of the Scopuli's destruction and the identity of the stealth ship involved is becoming clearer as the crew identifies a potential culprit near Eros."},{"name":"Protogen's Agenda","status":"active","characters":["Holden","Miller"],"summary":"Holden and Miller uncover Protogen's secretive and potentially dangerous experiments with the alien protomolecule, revealing the company's disregard for safety and ethical considerations."},{"name":"Stealth Ship Conflicts","status":"active","characters":["Holden","Amos","Naomi","Miller"],"summary":"The crew destroys the stealth ship to prevent an imminent explosion, and Miller reveals escalating conflict between Earth and Mars, implicating Holden's actions in sparking the battle."}],"summary":"Holden and his crew are aboard a dismantled stealth ship that they have repurposed, with the Earth and Mars engaged in significant conflict. Afte