."},{"name":"Dave","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"uncertain","lastSeen":"Prologue: Julie","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"The mechanic of Julie's ship; she describes him as someone who collects clips from old cartoons and knows a million jokes.","relationships":[{"character":"Julie Mao","relationship":"Shipmate and mechanic"},{"character":"Captain Darren","relationship":"Shipmate"},{"character":"Mike","relationship":"Shipmate"},{"character":"Wan Li","relationship":"Shipmate"}],"recentEvents":"Dave was heard to be in distress in an apparent torture situation, begging in a small broken voice."},{"name":"Captain Darren","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"uncertain","lastSeen":"Prologue: Julie","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"The captain of the Scopuli, who rolled over like a dog when the kidnappers arrived.","relationships":[{"character":"Julie Mao","relationship":"Captain of Julie's ship"},{"character":"Dave","relationship":"Shipmate and mechanic"},{"character":"Mike","relationship":"Shipmate"},{"character":"Wan Li","relationship":"Shipmate"}],"recentEvents":"Captain Darren's head appears fused to the reactor in an unknown form, asking for help, suggesting he is among those in the engineering deck."},{"name":"Mike","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"uncertain","lastSeen":"Prologue: Julie","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A shipmate of Julie's; no additional information provided in the text.","relationships":[{"character":"Julie Mao","relationship":"Shipmate"},{"character":"Dave","relationship":"Shipmate"},{"character":"Captain Darren","relationship":"Shipmate"},{"character":"Wan Li","relationship":"Shipmate"}],"recentEvents":"Mike was one of the shipmates who was taken by the kidnappers, but no specific events are detailed for him."},{"name":"Wan Li","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"uncertain","lastSeen":"Prologue: Julie","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A shipmate of J