ription":"A mariner with the Rocinante, primarily a medic and a pilot.","relationships":[{"character":"James Holden","relationship":"Captain and crew member"}],"recentEvents":"Lopez is not mentioned in this chapter."},{"name":"A marine officer","importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter: Tug of War","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A naval intelligence officer on the Donnager who questioned James Holden.","relationships":[{"character":"James Holden","relationship":"Interviewed subject"}],"recentEvents":"The officer questioned Holden and left his quarters during the battle."},{"name":"Dawes","aliases":["Agent Dawes"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter: Earth Is Pulling Out","currentLocation":"Ceres Station","description":"Station official often in discussions with Shaddid about station affairs and stability.","relationships":[{"character":"Shaddid","relationship":"Station official"},{"character":"Miller","relationship":"Contacts in station affairs"}],"recentEvents":"Was present in Shaddid's office for the announcement of Miller's firing and the new state of affairs."},{"name":"Hasini","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Drunk","currentLocation":"Ceres","description":"Owner of a bar named Blue Frog, helpful and concerned about the well-being of regular patrons like Miller.","relationships":[{"character":"James Miller","relationship":"Bar regular and patron"}],"recentEvents":"Helped a drunk and troubled Miller by taking him home in an electric cart."},{"name":"Lionel Polanski","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"","currentLocation":"Eros","description":"An imaginary owner of the Scopuli who checks into a flophouse.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Is a code name for an individual requiring covert assistance."},{"name":"Chang Chen Sematimba","aliases":["Chang","Semati"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Auburn and Beyond","currentLocation":"