cter":"James Holden","relationship":"Opponent, Negotiator"},{"character":"Naomi Nagata","relationship":"Opponent, Debater"}],"recentEvents":"Gave a detailed pitch to James Holden and his team about the necessity and potential of the Protogen project, including altering scientists to be high-functioning sociopaths."}],"locations":[{"name":"The Scopuli","aliases":["Scopuli"],"arc":"Piracy","description":"A ship that has been attacked and abandoned, located in the belt between planets.","recentEvents":"Jim and Amos investigate the ship and discover a fake distress beacon that led to the discovery of the derelict ship.","relationships":[{"location":"Knight","relationship":"Investigation crew arrives to the site of the distress call from Scopuli"}]},{"name":"Canterbury","aliases":["The Canterbury","Canter"],"arc":"War","description":"A commercial transport ship destroyed in a surprise attack.","recentEvents":"A group of survivors from the destroyed Canterbury have been rescued and are now being transported to safety, but they face new dangers aboard the ship.","relationships":[{"location":"Hangar Bay","relationship":"Part of the Canterbury where the survivors are hiding and trying to escape"}]},{"name":"CA-2216862","arc":"Emergency and Rescue","description":"A charted non-Belt asteroid near which the distressed Scopuli is located.","recentEvents":"The Scopuli is found in the vicinity of this asteroid in distress.","relationships":[{"location":"Scopuli","relationship":"Scopuli is located near it"}]},{"name":"Knight","aliases":["ship"],"arc":"The Protomolecule","description":"A ship belonging to the crew whose fate is entwined with the mysterious protomolecule and its effects.","recentEvents":"Crew received a message from Colonel Johnson, an influential figure in the Outer Planets Alliance, warning them against coercion and offering assistance if they need it.","relationships":[{"location":"Donnager","relationship":"Knight is being pursued by this Martian battlecruiser"},{